data.event: rrested were Darryl Keith Warden, 44, of 2517 Memphis St., Alexandria, and Sheila D. Williams, 41, of 420 Augusta St., Alexandria.
Around 7:35 p.m. Sunday Alexandria Police went to Warden’s Memphis Street home where Williams said she’d gone to pick up her daughter.
